WEBVTT

01:39.590 --> 01:43.190
[Road to Success]

01:44.539 --> 01:47.950
[Episode 25]

01:48.020 --> 01:50.950
[Entry]

02:51.840 --> 02:53.520
Has seeing the sea

02:55.240 --> 02:56.470
made you feel better?

03:21.150 --> 03:22.750
Is that Lin Wanxing?

03:22.750 --> 03:25.430
The one who seduced the professor
and became the other woman?

03:25.430 --> 03:26.960
Professor Shu is a good man.

03:26.960 --> 03:28.420
I even attended his class.

03:29.280 --> 03:31.030
Now look, it's all her fault.

03:31.030 --> 03:31.680
Let's go.

03:31.680 --> 03:32.470
Lin Wanxing.

03:32.470 --> 03:34.000
-It's really her.
-The one who seduced the professor.

03:34.000 --> 03:34.870
Shameless.

03:36.870 --> 03:38.370
[Withdrawal Application]

03:37.240 --> 03:38.079
Sign it.

03:38.800 --> 03:39.240
Mom,

03:39.910 --> 03:41.280
even you don't believe me.

03:41.280 --> 03:42.310
Sign it.

04:27.750 --> 04:29.700
Saying out your sad things

04:31.840 --> 04:33.570
will make you feel a bit better.

04:39.510 --> 04:41.440
When my grandpa was seriously ill,

04:43.750 --> 04:45.390
my parents locked me at home

04:46.920 --> 04:48.360
and wouldn't let me out.

04:54.800 --> 04:56.190
After he passed away,

04:59.140 --> 05:00.900
they didn't tell me

05:04.160 --> 05:06.360
or even let me go to his funeral.

05:06.800 --> 05:07.950
Where is Grandpa?

05:07.950 --> 05:08.800
I want to see him!

05:08.800 --> 05:10.460
He has already been cremated.

05:13.390 --> 05:14.240
What?

05:17.800 --> 05:19.510
Why didn't you tell me?

05:20.520 --> 05:22.320
Why didn't you tell me?

05:23.680 --> 05:24.810
Where are you going?

05:28.270 --> 05:29.600
In this world,

05:31.630 --> 05:34.030
only Grandpa and Grandma
loved me the most.

05:39.510 --> 05:41.110
I don't even dare to imagine,

05:43.680 --> 05:45.680
before Grandpa passed away,

05:47.800 --> 05:49.920
not seeing me for the last time,

05:52.159 --> 05:54.159
how disappointed he must have been.

05:58.640 --> 06:01.560
I really hate myself.

06:13.160 --> 06:14.650
Do you remember

06:17.350 --> 06:19.410
the day the photography studio owner

06:20.480 --> 06:21.720
delivered your grandparents' wedding photo

06:21.720 --> 06:22.950
to you?

06:24.730 --> 06:25.500
He said

06:26.280 --> 06:27.410
that he

06:28.480 --> 06:30.040
and many neighbors

06:31.660 --> 06:33.659
were your grandparents' students.

06:36.310 --> 06:38.680
Your grandparents
had students all over the world,

06:38.680 --> 06:40.610
but never collected a single cent.

06:41.000 --> 06:43.730
How could your grandparents
with such great love

06:45.120 --> 06:46.880
blame you?

06:49.480 --> 06:52.140
Even though you didn't see
him for the last time,

06:52.670 --> 06:54.530
they will definitely understand

06:56.880 --> 06:58.610
your feelings and affections.

07:24.800 --> 07:25.630
Don't cry.

07:26.600 --> 07:28.260
Let's go to the beach to relax.

08:26.830 --> 08:27.950
If you still feel bad,

08:27.950 --> 08:29.750
do you want to grab some wontons?

08:30.270 --> 08:32.200
My parents are still waiting for me.

08:32.200 --> 08:34.860
I have to go back
and solve the problem with them.

08:38.120 --> 08:39.320
What's your thought?

08:40.789 --> 08:41.980
I will not resign,

08:42.679 --> 08:44.410
and I will not go back with them.

08:51.760 --> 08:53.240
Central Cannon.

08:53.270 --> 08:53.930
Checkmate.

08:54.670 --> 08:56.070
What's going on?

09:03.870 --> 09:05.240
You're finally here.

09:06.750 --> 09:07.750
Hey, pretty girl.

09:08.870 --> 09:10.030
Why are you here?

09:10.030 --> 09:11.970
Well, you reacted quite fast.

09:12.090 --> 09:14.050
And who is this?

09:15.640 --> 09:17.070
Don't be afraid, Ms. Lin.

09:18.000 --> 09:18.800
This is my dad.

09:20.690 --> 09:21.760
Hello, Uncle.

09:21.790 --> 09:22.910
I'm Lin Wanxing.

09:23.120 --> 09:24.670
Lin Wanxing.

09:25.440 --> 09:26.670
Wan, as in sunset glow?

09:26.670 --> 09:27.930
Xing, as in starry sky?

09:27.950 --> 09:29.340
That's a good name.

09:29.390 --> 09:32.470
Stop to enjoy the maple woods at dusk;

09:32.470 --> 09:34.240
last night's stars and last night's wind.

09:34.240 --> 09:35.720
Apes calling endlessly from both banks;

09:35.720 --> 09:37.960
looking different from far and near,
high and low.

09:37.960 --> 09:39.030
I have inspiration.

09:39.030 --> 09:40.120
Memorize it.

09:40.120 --> 09:41.750
I'll send it to your mom when I'm back.

09:41.750 --> 09:42.510
Mom must be rushing you.

09:42.510 --> 09:43.320
Dad, you should go home.

09:43.320 --> 09:43.840
Go home?

09:43.840 --> 09:45.790
I get inspiration
when I see a pretty girl.

09:45.790 --> 09:46.840
Girl, um,

09:46.840 --> 09:47.550
it's so hot today.

09:47.550 --> 09:50.100
Can I go to your house for a cup of tea?

09:51.200 --> 09:52.480
Yes, you can,

09:52.480 --> 09:53.870
Uncle,

09:53.870 --> 09:55.200
but my parents are home too.

09:55.200 --> 09:55.720
That's wonderful.

09:55.720 --> 09:57.600
I can pay a visit to your parents.

09:59.720 --> 10:00.650
Which door is it?

10:02.630 --> 10:04.130
I'll open the door for you.

10:04.150 --> 10:06.820
Your house looks retro and romantic.

10:07.550 --> 10:09.960
Wang Fa, what are you standing there for?

10:10.840 --> 10:11.670
We're here.

10:11.670 --> 10:14.630
What are you doing? Do you want
to let me die of thirst? Let's go.

10:14.630 --> 10:15.480
Let's go. Let's go.

10:15.480 --> 10:16.440
Have you got everything?

10:16.440 --> 10:17.120
Is there anything else left in the car?

10:17.120 --> 10:17.750
Keep up, come on.

10:17.750 --> 10:18.720
Nothing else.

10:28.150 --> 10:29.610
Don't waste any more time.

10:30.010 --> 10:31.740
You come back with me right now.

10:34.030 --> 10:35.440
Did you hear me talking to you?

10:35.440 --> 10:36.150
You're a big boy now.

10:36.150 --> 10:36.910
What are you shy about?

10:36.910 --> 10:37.670
-Let's go. Come in.
-Dad.

10:37.670 --> 10:38.630
Come in and sit.

10:39.440 --> 10:40.270
Well...

10:41.790 --> 10:44.320
You must be Lin Wanxing's parents.

10:44.340 --> 10:47.430
Well-educated people
just have a different vibe.

10:47.600 --> 10:49.030
No wonder Wanxing has

10:49.030 --> 10:50.200
all the finest qualities.

10:50.200 --> 10:52.440
Like father, like daughter.

10:52.440 --> 10:53.790
Nice to meet you.

10:55.750 --> 10:56.630
Wanxing is excellent,

10:56.630 --> 10:58.270
and our Wang Fa is not bad either.

10:58.270 --> 10:59.200
Don't mind how I am,

10:59.200 --> 11:01.220
but my son takes after his mother.

11:01.440 --> 11:03.030
His mother's genes are incredibly strong.

11:03.030 --> 11:04.110
Absolutely top-notch.

11:04.110 --> 11:06.040
You must believe this, my in-laws.

11:08.440 --> 11:09.720
Watch my dad perform.

11:11.360 --> 11:13.440
This is your son?

11:13.440 --> 11:14.320
Yes.

11:14.320 --> 11:15.080
As far as I know,

11:15.080 --> 11:17.040
he and my daughter are not that close.

11:17.040 --> 11:18.080
He's her tenant

11:18.080 --> 11:19.200
and colleague.

11:19.200 --> 11:21.530
And we couldn't possibly be your in-laws.

11:23.150 --> 11:24.550
Well, everything in the world

11:24.550 --> 11:26.200
is constantly developing,

11:26.200 --> 11:26.910
isn't it?

11:27.600 --> 11:28.670
Let's not stand and talk.

11:28.670 --> 11:30.510
Sit down and talk.
Why are you being so polite?

11:30.510 --> 11:31.390
-Don't.
-Sit down.

11:31.390 --> 11:32.030
Don't be polite.

11:32.030 --> 11:33.000
Sit. Sit.

11:33.000 --> 11:34.600
Sit. Let's sit down and talk.

11:34.910 --> 11:35.550
Yes.

11:35.570 --> 11:36.450
Put them here.

11:39.270 --> 11:40.030
Well,

11:40.270 --> 11:42.080
a little token of my appreciation.

11:42.080 --> 11:43.280
I don't accept gifts.

11:44.150 --> 11:45.120
They're not really gifts,

11:45.120 --> 11:46.200
just some local specialties.

11:46.200 --> 11:47.030
Sorry,

11:47.750 --> 11:48.950
it's inappropriate.

11:49.720 --> 11:51.000
Understood.

11:51.510 --> 11:53.030
Let's put the gifts aside for now.

11:53.030 --> 11:54.200
The main purpose of my visit

11:54.200 --> 11:55.720
is to ask you

11:55.720 --> 11:59.550
to marry your daughter to my son.

12:07.030 --> 12:08.710
Marriage is a big deal.

12:09.240 --> 12:11.230
It's not children playing house.

12:11.480 --> 12:13.180
Besides, in our Lin family,

12:13.480 --> 12:14.600
we have rules.

12:14.620 --> 12:15.380
Yes.

12:16.750 --> 12:17.480
Wanxing,

12:17.860 --> 12:20.750
what exactly is your relationship
with your colleague?

12:20.750 --> 12:22.240
Why did you hide it from us?

12:25.200 --> 12:26.200
Uncle, Aunt,

12:26.840 --> 12:27.670
I'm sorry.

12:29.080 --> 12:31.140
Actually, I'm pursuing Lin Wanxing,

12:31.430 --> 12:33.160
and she just hasn't agreed yet.

12:38.930 --> 12:39.790
How about this?

12:40.120 --> 12:42.710
If you don't want
to marry off your daughter,

12:43.210 --> 12:44.560
we can come to you.

12:45.080 --> 12:47.010
Wang Fa can marry into your family.

12:47.150 --> 12:47.840
But

12:47.840 --> 12:50.000
I need to go back
and ask my wife for permission.

12:50.000 --> 12:50.960
I have to report to her.

12:50.960 --> 12:52.760
Aren't you just messing around?

12:53.000 --> 12:53.480
Lin.

12:53.480 --> 12:54.750
-Are you not feeling well?
-What's wrong?

12:54.750 --> 12:56.320
My dad has a heart condition.

12:56.320 --> 12:57.910
This is bad.
Let's go to the hospital right away.

12:57.910 --> 12:59.150
-Hurry.
-I'll go get the medicine.

12:59.150 --> 13:00.150
What medicine?

13:00.150 --> 13:00.670
Let me catch my breath.

13:00.670 --> 13:01.670
Health is the most important thing.

13:01.670 --> 13:02.370
No need.

13:02.390 --> 13:04.590
-I'm fine.
-You should be more careful.

13:05.320 --> 13:06.250
Really, no need.

13:07.600 --> 13:08.080
Ma,

13:08.080 --> 13:09.640
call Director Xu.

13:09.820 --> 13:10.410
Yes.

13:10.730 --> 13:11.720
You guys don't need to go with us.

13:11.720 --> 13:12.200
Don't.

13:12.200 --> 13:12.960
Leave it to me.

13:12.960 --> 13:14.080
No problem. No problem.

13:14.080 --> 13:14.910
But...

13:15.790 --> 13:17.910
but it's not that serious.

13:28.270 --> 13:30.800
Everything has been arranged
as you ordered.

13:31.120 --> 13:32.320
Careful, careful.

13:32.600 --> 13:34.200
This is our most distinguished guest.

13:34.200 --> 13:35.080
Take good care of him.

13:35.080 --> 13:35.810
Please.

13:40.100 --> 13:42.210
[Hengjiu Hospital]

13:43.000 --> 13:44.000
This way, please.

13:44.480 --> 13:45.030
Please.

13:46.200 --> 13:49.790
The time when my son
needs me has finally arrived.

13:56.120 --> 13:57.120
Here, coffee.

13:57.120 --> 13:58.080
No need.

13:58.120 --> 13:59.360
By the way, do you want sugar?

13:59.360 --> 14:00.320
-No need.
-Really?

14:00.320 --> 14:01.870
Okay, okay.

14:03.910 --> 14:04.510
I'll do it.

14:04.510 --> 14:06.110
This outfit fits quite well.

14:07.550 --> 14:08.580
Mr. Wang.

14:09.360 --> 14:10.870
Who exactly are you?

14:11.460 --> 14:13.240
I haven't made it clear, have I?

14:14.540 --> 14:16.180
I am Wang Genfa,

14:16.200 --> 14:17.630
Chairman of Hengjiu Group.

14:17.630 --> 14:19.350
This hospital is owned by me.

14:21.000 --> 14:22.320
T-This is my...

14:23.770 --> 14:24.810
Weibo account.

14:25.040 --> 14:27.070
[Wang Genfa]

14:25.430 --> 14:26.400
Wang Genfa.

14:26.430 --> 14:27.360
A verified user.

14:27.360 --> 14:29.220
I have over 20 million followers.

14:30.750 --> 14:31.510
I am

14:31.510 --> 14:33.770
quite outgoing

14:33.800 --> 14:35.350
and very determined.

14:35.390 --> 14:36.390
Our Wang Fa

14:36.390 --> 14:38.480
has fully inherited my traits.

14:38.480 --> 14:39.870
Especially his mother's

14:39.870 --> 14:42.980
genes of intelligence and beauty.

14:43.010 --> 14:44.520
So I think my son

14:44.550 --> 14:46.580
and your daughter, Ms. Lin,

14:46.600 --> 14:47.880
are quite a good match.

14:47.910 --> 14:49.570
What do you think, my in-laws?

14:50.240 --> 14:51.240
Mr. Wang,

14:51.240 --> 14:53.030
the kids
haven't even started anything yet.

14:53.030 --> 14:54.480
It's inappropriate
to address us like that.

14:54.480 --> 14:55.450
Yes.

14:55.920 --> 14:58.340
Then I'll just call you Lin.

14:59.310 --> 15:00.190
Lin.

15:01.010 --> 15:01.850
Come in.

15:03.870 --> 15:05.200
Chairman, everything is ready.

15:05.200 --> 15:05.790
Come on.

15:06.270 --> 15:06.910
Let's do a checkup.

15:06.910 --> 15:07.960
No, it's not necessary.

15:07.960 --> 15:08.720
You are already here.

15:08.720 --> 15:10.360
-Mr. Wang. Mr. Wang.
-You're already here.

15:10.360 --> 15:11.630
-No need.
-Take your blood pressure first.

15:11.630 --> 15:12.720
Take your blood pressure first.

15:12.720 --> 15:15.120
-I'm really fine.
-Hurry up.

15:16.390 --> 15:18.120
Don't worry, Lin.

15:18.120 --> 15:19.200
If you leave your daughter to our family,

15:19.200 --> 15:21.120
I'll treat her better
than my own daughter.

15:21.120 --> 15:22.120
-Wait.
-Stop talking.

15:22.120 --> 15:23.460
She's taking your blood pressure.

15:23.460 --> 15:25.790
Later, there will be blood oxygen tests
and an ECG.

15:25.790 --> 15:27.420
Director Xu, schedule all the tests.

15:27.420 --> 15:29.060
Yes, everything is ready.

15:34.120 --> 15:34.950
[Left lower limb]

15:51.080 --> 15:52.030
In short,

15:52.030 --> 15:53.360
we have plenty of money.

15:53.900 --> 15:54.640
Lin,

15:54.940 --> 15:56.030
the two kids

15:56.030 --> 15:57.600
grew up in different surroundings

15:57.600 --> 15:59.320
and had very different upbringings,

15:59.320 --> 16:01.080
but they are fated.

16:01.080 --> 16:02.600
They share the same ambitions,

16:02.600 --> 16:04.700
wishes, and ideals.

16:05.030 --> 16:06.270
-They're fated means...
-Wait.

16:06.270 --> 16:08.030
It takes hundreds of years
of good deeds to cross the same river,

16:08.030 --> 16:10.150
and thousands to sleep in the same bed,

16:10.150 --> 16:10.750
right?

16:11.380 --> 16:12.300
So,

16:12.330 --> 16:14.070
as parents,

16:14.090 --> 16:16.960
we should give them
more understanding and support.

16:16.960 --> 16:18.360
These are words
from the bottom of my heart,

16:18.360 --> 16:19.360
truly heartfelt.

16:21.530 --> 16:22.480
Lin.

16:23.150 --> 16:23.750
Lin.

16:24.360 --> 16:24.840
Look.

16:24.840 --> 16:28.110
There are many reports
online about Lin Wanxing's team.

16:28.280 --> 16:30.220
The new supervisor of Hongjing No. 8 High,

16:30.220 --> 16:33.120
Lin Wanxing, has led the team
to a successful comeback.

16:33.120 --> 16:33.930
[I Never Taught Them How to Win,]

16:33.950 --> 16:35.110
[But They Taught Me Not to Run Away]

16:34.670 --> 16:35.320
Look.

16:35.130 --> 16:36.640
[Lin Wanxing:
Four Seasons with a Boys' Team]

16:38.680 --> 16:39.430
[Behind the Success
of Hongjing No. 8 High's Football Team]

16:39.470 --> 16:40.110
[She Had No Football Background,
Yet Built a Miracle Team]

16:39.880 --> 16:42.180
Wanxing is really promising.

16:40.160 --> 16:40.500
[Lin Wanxing and the Boys
of Hongjing No. 8 High:]

16:40.500 --> 16:40.840
[A True Underdog Comeback Story]

16:40.860 --> 16:41.410
[I Never Taught Them How to Win,]

16:41.430 --> 16:42.390
[But They Taught Me Not to Run Away]

16:42.580 --> 16:44.070
A born champion.

16:45.460 --> 16:45.780
[She Had No Football Background,
Yet Built a Miracle Team]

16:45.810 --> 16:45.940
[Lin Wanxing and the Boys
of Hongjing No. 8 High:]

16:45.940 --> 16:46.080
[A True Underdog Comeback Story]

16:46.320 --> 16:46.700
[On the grass pitch
within Hongjing No. 8 High's campus,]

16:46.720 --> 16:47.180
[there stands a team reshaping everyone's

16:47.200 --> 16:47.540
[perception of school football.]

16:48.110 --> 16:49.940
But then again,

16:49.960 --> 16:52.590
with such high media attention right now,

16:52.730 --> 16:55.900
if Wanxing suddenly resigns at this time,

16:56.440 --> 16:58.040
what impact would that have?

16:58.630 --> 17:00.390
If the media

17:00.390 --> 17:01.240
gossips

17:01.240 --> 17:03.390
and digs deep,
who knows what they'll find,

17:03.390 --> 17:04.160
right?

17:06.280 --> 17:06.990
Mr. Wang.

17:08.030 --> 17:09.790
Are you threatening me?

17:09.790 --> 17:10.790
Well,

17:10.790 --> 17:12.160
how is that possible? No.

17:12.160 --> 17:13.640
We're one.

17:14.200 --> 17:15.310
I just think

17:15.310 --> 17:17.030
it's a good thing
for our kids to be famous.

17:17.030 --> 17:18.680
It not only brings honor to the ancestors,

17:18.680 --> 17:21.130
but it also helps your career, right?

17:23.000 --> 17:24.680
It's not just your Wanxing
who is excellent.

17:24.680 --> 17:26.540
Our Wang family isn't bad either.

17:26.680 --> 17:27.619
Look at this.

17:28.830 --> 17:30.000
Hengjiu's hotels.

17:32.170 --> 17:33.930
To be frank,

17:34.070 --> 17:37.040
Hengjiu's hotels are top-notch globally.

17:37.290 --> 17:39.570
When the time comes, we can join forces.

17:39.600 --> 17:40.640
I have decided

17:40.660 --> 17:41.890
to invest right in Baiyu

17:41.890 --> 17:42.560
in

17:42.590 --> 17:44.310
a super five-star AI hotel.

17:44.720 --> 17:47.780
You can cut the ribbon
at the groundbreaking ceremony.

17:48.680 --> 17:50.510
Then I'll get Ma, um,

17:50.510 --> 17:51.240
Director Ma,

17:51.880 --> 17:52.720
to join us.

17:52.720 --> 17:53.450
How about it?

17:54.880 --> 17:55.960
You know

17:56.880 --> 17:57.610
Director Ma?

17:57.960 --> 17:59.110
I know him too well.

17:59.110 --> 18:00.830
He chases after me every day,

18:00.830 --> 18:01.790
asking for investments,

18:01.790 --> 18:03.000
and I haven't agreed.

18:03.000 --> 18:03.510
Then...

18:03.510 --> 18:05.480
now... now...

18:05.740 --> 18:07.620
Now, I can clearly tell him that

18:08.070 --> 18:09.790
because of you,

18:10.200 --> 18:11.720
I can cooperate with him.

18:17.370 --> 18:18.040
By the way,

18:18.590 --> 18:20.480
I've booked the flights for you.

18:20.480 --> 18:22.310
8:00 a.m. tomorrow.

18:22.340 --> 18:24.530
First class to Baiyu, how's that?

18:24.550 --> 18:25.910
Tomorrow morning?

18:25.930 --> 18:26.900
Later, then?

18:27.740 --> 18:29.020
Tomorrow, we...

18:29.070 --> 18:30.260
might as well go back first.

18:30.260 --> 18:32.320
I still have a lot of things to handle.

18:32.400 --> 18:34.130
That works. It's settled then.

18:34.290 --> 18:35.090
Then...

18:35.120 --> 18:35.840
Mr. Wang.

18:41.460 --> 18:42.490
It's settled then.

18:42.490 --> 18:44.380
Chairman, everything is ready.

18:44.410 --> 18:46.210
Alright, go on.

18:46.230 --> 18:48.190
I've arranged a full checkup for you.

18:48.190 --> 18:49.850
There are still 18 items left.

18:50.440 --> 18:51.510
I'm fine.

18:51.510 --> 18:52.810
I'm in good health.

18:52.880 --> 18:54.000
-Mr. Wang.
-No harm in extra check-ups.

18:54.000 --> 18:55.790
-I can't stand it anymore!
-No harm in extra check-ups.

18:55.790 --> 18:56.680
I've arranged everything.

18:56.680 --> 18:58.960
You don't have to pay, don't worry.

19:05.750 --> 19:06.750
Got it.

19:12.950 --> 19:14.320
My dad said

19:14.670 --> 19:17.130
he's leaving first thing tomorrow morning.

19:17.140 --> 19:18.450
How did your dad do it?

19:18.960 --> 19:20.960
The stubborn lose to the cunning.

19:21.870 --> 19:24.070
My dad is the best at persuading people.

19:24.590 --> 19:26.590
Sorry for troubling your dad today.

19:26.760 --> 19:28.560
They came so suddenly this time.

19:29.460 --> 19:31.660
I hadn't figured out how to deal with it.

19:37.660 --> 19:39.180
This afternoon,

19:39.830 --> 19:41.180
you didn't look well.

19:43.790 --> 19:45.520
Are you feeling any better now?

19:47.060 --> 19:47.890
Much better.

19:56.440 --> 19:58.500
The moonlight is beautiful tonight.

19:59.030 --> 20:00.090
Let's go for a walk.

20:04.590 --> 20:05.510
Actually...

20:07.360 --> 20:08.430
I have a gift

20:09.610 --> 20:10.520
that I've been thinking about

20:10.520 --> 20:12.200
giving you on your birthday.

20:13.530 --> 20:14.580
But now,

20:14.640 --> 20:16.170
I want to give it to you early

20:17.340 --> 20:19.010
to make you

20:19.830 --> 20:20.550
smile.

20:27.030 --> 20:28.680
Rainbow Bear Park?

20:28.980 --> 20:30.980
Hasn't this place been closed down?

20:32.890 --> 20:34.810
Why did you think of bringing me here?

20:34.810 --> 20:35.720
Didn't you say

20:35.720 --> 20:38.110
your grandpa used to bring you here
a lot when you were little?

20:38.110 --> 20:39.160
When I looked at
your photo album last time,

20:39.160 --> 20:40.880
there was a picture
of you sitting in a teacup ride,

20:40.880 --> 20:42.350
grinning from ear to ear.

20:42.350 --> 20:43.070
Indeed.

20:43.070 --> 20:45.310
I used to come here
every week when I was little.

20:45.310 --> 20:46.640
Grandpa would take pictures of me

20:46.640 --> 20:48.300
and take me on the teacup ride.

20:48.830 --> 20:49.690
And over there.

20:52.030 --> 20:53.110
This whole area used to be

20:53.110 --> 20:54.440
full of food stalls.

20:54.440 --> 20:55.880
There were so many delicious foods.

20:55.880 --> 20:56.880
There were grilled sausages,

20:56.880 --> 20:58.000
fried chicken,

20:58.000 --> 20:59.240
tea eggs,

20:59.550 --> 21:00.550
and cotton candy.

21:00.550 --> 21:02.510
Cotton candy was my favorite.

21:02.510 --> 21:03.480
Every time I finished eating it,

21:03.480 --> 21:05.260
my mouth would be all sticky.

21:05.790 --> 21:06.960
And that too.

21:07.400 --> 21:08.110
Look.

21:08.110 --> 21:10.440
I also loved this flying car ride
when I was little.

21:10.440 --> 21:11.840
Besides the teacup ride,

21:12.110 --> 21:13.770
what other rides did you like?

21:13.830 --> 21:16.030
The carousel, of course.

21:16.440 --> 21:18.880
But there was always a long line,

21:18.880 --> 21:21.340
so I didn't get to ride it
many times in total.

21:25.590 --> 21:26.720
Where are you going?

21:28.070 --> 21:28.920
Wang Fa?

21:31.720 --> 21:32.470
Wang Fa?

21:36.000 --> 21:36.790
Wang Fa?

21:38.750 --> 21:39.610
Where did he go?

21:40.590 --> 21:41.590
Wang Fa!

21:54.050 --> 21:56.120
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

21:56.590 --> 21:58.960
♪ On the summer night ♪

21:59.440 --> 22:04.950
♪ Like stars that glow so bright ♪

22:06.470 --> 22:08.730
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

22:09.440 --> 22:15.230
♪ Lost in a dream secretly ♪

22:18.840 --> 22:23.960
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

22:22.080 --> 22:23.210
Want to give it a try?

22:24.690 --> 22:30.070
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

22:30.910 --> 22:33.210
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

22:33.880 --> 22:39.700
♪ And spreading into
a gentle sea of stars ♪

22:35.260 --> 22:36.020
Sit tight.

22:39.870 --> 22:40.870
It starts to spin.

22:42.940 --> 22:44.770
♪ Every night ♪

22:45.690 --> 22:47.660
♪ I reach for starlight ♪

22:48.310 --> 22:50.350
This amusement park
has been abandoned for a long time.

22:48.560 --> 22:50.390
♪ Wandering through dreams with you ♪

22:50.880 --> 22:52.320
I know

22:50.960 --> 22:53.170
♪ I follow the beat of my heart ♪

22:52.350 --> 22:53.830
you must have spent a lot of effort

22:53.830 --> 22:55.180
redoing the circuits

22:54.340 --> 22:56.920
♪ Like dust floating in the air ♪

22:55.480 --> 22:58.190
to make this carousel spin again.

22:57.940 --> 22:59.740
♪ Because of your love ♪

22:58.750 --> 22:59.440
Wang Fa,

23:00.050 --> 23:01.180
thank you.

23:00.630 --> 23:05.000
♪ I shine brilliantly ♪

23:01.240 --> 23:03.030
To be able to see your smile

23:03.720 --> 23:05.160
makes it all worth it.

23:28.200 --> 23:30.600
Actually, I have one more thing
to give you.

23:30.640 --> 23:31.240
What is it?

23:38.070 --> 23:39.030
Is this...

23:45.920 --> 23:47.400
A Hundred Wishes?

23:48.070 --> 23:48.750
Open it.

23:55.830 --> 23:57.070
Restore lost ancient techniques.

23:57.070 --> 23:58.070
Survive in the wild
for 7 consecutive days.

23:58.070 --> 23:59.350
Establish a stray animal shelter.

23:59.350 --> 24:00.960
See the aurora in the Arctic Circle.

24:00.960 --> 24:02.350
Learn sign language
and communicate with the disabled.

24:02.350 --> 24:03.350
Complete 1,000 hours of volunteer service.

24:03.350 --> 24:05.030
Collect 108 city landmarks.

24:05.030 --> 24:07.110
-Complete a full marathon.
-Be together

24:06.010 --> 24:12.040
[Be together with Ms. Lin]

24:08.310 --> 24:09.510
with Ms. Lin.

24:17.550 --> 24:18.480
There were

24:22.160 --> 24:24.570
countless moments
I wanted to say this to you.

24:24.570 --> 24:26.830
♪ Two souls aligned ♪

24:28.440 --> 24:30.560
♪ In silent gravity ♪

24:28.970 --> 24:30.100
I like you.

24:32.600 --> 24:34.800
♪ Heal my heart ♪

24:35.110 --> 24:36.030
Will you

24:35.340 --> 24:37.960
♪ With every part of you ♪

24:37.640 --> 24:38.590
be with me?

24:39.240 --> 24:40.130
But...

24:40.530 --> 24:42.520
♪ Our words flow ♪

24:42.440 --> 24:44.000
I've got so many issues.

24:44.000 --> 24:46.000
♪ A gentle stream ♪

24:46.670 --> 24:48.310
Everyone's got their own problems.

24:48.310 --> 24:50.490
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

24:51.030 --> 24:51.720
I...

24:51.140 --> 24:53.660
♪ Inside a silken dream ♪

24:51.720 --> 24:53.450
I-I still have a lot of secrets.

24:54.790 --> 24:57.110
And there are many things
I don't want to tell you.

24:55.870 --> 25:01.780
♪ We talk the cool night, breeze away ♪

24:57.170 --> 24:58.300
I've said it before.

24:58.680 --> 25:00.610
You have the right to keep secrets.

25:02.510 --> 25:03.640
You also know

25:03.700 --> 25:05.320
♪ We trace the roads ♪

25:04.070 --> 25:06.100
my family relationships
are very complicated.

25:06.100 --> 25:09.210
♪ That never see an end ♪

25:06.840 --> 25:08.730
If we're to buy our first home
in the future

25:08.730 --> 25:10.790
and split the down payment half-and-half,

25:10.790 --> 25:12.460
I won't be able to afford it.

25:11.890 --> 25:15.300
♪ We softly calm the hidden doubt ♪

25:12.480 --> 25:14.210
I don't want to hide it from you.

25:15.310 --> 25:16.680
Then I can just continue renting.

25:16.090 --> 25:20.700
♪ Seen in each other's eyes ♪

25:18.840 --> 25:20.230
Are you...

25:21.000 --> 25:22.590
trying to keep freeloading?

25:21.360 --> 25:25.330
♪ And wake the warmth inside ♪

25:23.270 --> 25:24.260
You caught me.

25:26.110 --> 25:27.030
I also...

25:27.280 --> 25:29.840
♪ Life begins alone ♪

25:27.410 --> 25:28.210
have many...

25:30.390 --> 25:33.300
♪ A road we walk alone ♪

25:35.030 --> 25:36.030
You're good.

25:35.200 --> 25:37.420
♪ Until fate brings warmth ♪

25:38.020 --> 25:41.460
♪ To light our way back home ♪

25:38.530 --> 25:40.530
Everything about you is wonderful.

25:43.570 --> 25:45.270
♪ True love is not just ♪

25:45.270 --> 25:46.970
You don't have to answer me right now.

25:46.030 --> 25:47.630
♪ The gaze when two hearts first meet ♪

25:48.070 --> 25:49.350
I don't want to pressure you.

25:48.540 --> 25:53.430
♪ It's courage in the arms ♪

25:51.790 --> 25:53.340
I just want you to know

25:54.400 --> 25:56.920
that besides your grandparents
in this world,

25:55.350 --> 25:57.730
♪ We stand as one ♪

25:59.100 --> 26:00.710
there is someone else who loves you.

25:59.120 --> 26:01.350
♪ Our words flow ♪

26:02.740 --> 26:04.950
♪ A gentle stream ♪

26:06.890 --> 26:09.350
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

26:09.720 --> 26:12.360
♪ Inside a silken dream ♪

26:14.820 --> 26:20.620
♪ We talk the cool night, breeze away ♪

26:18.680 --> 26:19.480
Lin Wanxing,

26:22.060 --> 26:23.740
-you…
-No need to think about it.

26:23.740 --> 26:25.270
I'll answer you now.

26:26.370 --> 26:28.520
♪ Life begins alone ♪

26:29.510 --> 26:32.110
♪ A road we walk alone ♪

26:34.060 --> 26:36.340
♪ Until fate brings warmth ♪

26:37.140 --> 26:40.470
♪ To light our way back home ♪

26:42.580 --> 26:44.010
♪ True love is not just ♪

26:45.080 --> 26:46.410
♪ The gaze when two hearts first meet ♪

26:47.520 --> 26:52.300
♪ It's courage in the arms ♪

26:54.300 --> 26:57.350
♪ We stand as one ♪

27:06.750 --> 27:12.290
♪And all ♪

27:10.670 --> 27:14.390
[Administrative Building]

27:11.890 --> 27:14.700
Yongchuan Hengjiu
beat Yuzhou Yinxiang yesterday.

27:14.700 --> 27:15.700
Six points.

27:15.720 --> 27:17.440
I knew I was the chosen one.

27:17.470 --> 27:19.360
Let's talk after we beat Shenhai Yinbo.

27:19.360 --> 27:20.200
So,

27:20.220 --> 27:21.340
we need extra training.

27:21.340 --> 27:22.510
-Come on.
-I'll use the restroom,

27:22.510 --> 27:23.270
then come back for extra training.

27:23.270 --> 27:23.810
-Okay.
-Okay.

27:23.810 --> 27:25.340
-Hurry up.
-Come back soon.

27:25.400 --> 27:26.330
Extra training.

27:28.350 --> 27:29.350
Oh my god.

27:29.350 --> 27:31.100
Guys, come here.

27:32.310 --> 27:33.110
What's wrong?

27:36.270 --> 27:38.000
Look, look.

27:38.000 --> 27:39.310
Look there.

27:44.880 --> 27:46.590
Something big is coming up ahead.

27:46.590 --> 27:47.480
Wait,

27:47.480 --> 27:48.990
what's the big fuss?

27:50.980 --> 27:53.780
Isn't it just Coach
bringing Ms. Lin some food?

27:54.110 --> 27:55.400
Boss,

27:55.400 --> 27:58.590
with your observation skills,
how are you going to woo Bao Xiaotian?

27:58.590 --> 28:00.790
Romance is in the air today.

28:04.160 --> 28:05.360
Let me wipe it for you.

28:05.550 --> 28:06.790
I'll do it myself.

28:08.550 --> 28:09.160
Alright. Alright.

28:09.160 --> 28:10.640
Go to your training.

28:10.640 --> 28:12.700
So many people are watching outside.

28:14.270 --> 28:14.800
Okay.

28:15.070 --> 28:16.130
You eat first then.

28:18.510 --> 28:20.100
-Hurry and leave.
-Hurry and leave.

28:20.100 --> 28:22.100
-Hurry and leave.
-Hurry and leave.

28:32.000 --> 28:32.590
Coach.

28:32.590 --> 28:33.300
-Hello, Coach.
-Hello, Coach.

28:33.300 --> 28:35.030
-Hello, Coach.
-Hello, Coach.

28:35.750 --> 28:36.550
Good morning.

28:36.910 --> 28:37.870
Coach,

28:38.710 --> 28:40.820
Lu said you managed to woo Ms. Lin.

28:40.840 --> 28:42.040
Is it true?

28:42.070 --> 28:43.680
How could I be wrong?

28:43.680 --> 28:45.740
Besides, wasn't everyone watching?

28:46.590 --> 28:47.270
Coach,

28:47.270 --> 28:48.240
are you and Ms. Lin

28:48.240 --> 28:50.680
going to get a marriage certificate?

28:53.840 --> 28:55.250
A-Alright.

28:55.640 --> 28:56.440
Get ready for training.

28:56.440 --> 28:57.110
Coach,

28:57.880 --> 28:59.010
are you stuttering?

29:00.750 --> 29:01.960
I'm not stuttering.

29:01.960 --> 29:03.030
If you aren't,

29:03.030 --> 29:04.560
why is your chin trembling?

29:14.360 --> 29:15.080
Lin Lu.

29:16.220 --> 29:17.630
Yousuanru.

29:23.550 --> 29:24.210
Is it sweet?

29:25.840 --> 29:27.500
Sweet and sour, so delicious.

29:34.240 --> 29:35.170
Start training.

29:36.200 --> 29:37.880
Time for training!

29:37.880 --> 29:39.070
Training!

29:40.650 --> 29:42.430
The smell of love!

29:46.880 --> 29:48.040
Come on!

29:48.350 --> 29:49.240
How is it?

29:49.240 --> 29:51.110
Did what I tell you this afternoon

29:51.110 --> 29:52.440
give you a wake-up call?

29:54.240 --> 29:55.480
Chengye.

29:56.200 --> 29:57.290
Why are you here?

29:58.440 --> 30:00.590
Are you here to hand in your assignment?

30:00.590 --> 30:02.390
Ms. Lin, I haven't decided yet.

30:03.400 --> 30:05.000
That's fine. Take your time.

30:11.550 --> 30:12.680
Are you here for him?

30:15.720 --> 30:16.590
Take your time talking.

30:16.590 --> 30:17.920
I'll wait for you ahead.

30:23.030 --> 30:24.920
Since you came here specifically for me,

30:24.920 --> 30:26.980
do you have any new ideas for the team?

30:29.480 --> 30:31.010
I can't say for sure either.

30:32.680 --> 30:34.030
Do you think our team

30:34.350 --> 30:35.510
can win right now?

30:36.270 --> 30:37.270
Do you want to win?

30:38.550 --> 30:39.210
I can't say.

30:41.510 --> 30:43.240
Then tell me what you can say.

30:45.870 --> 30:48.550
I don't think I'm suited
for my current position.

30:48.550 --> 30:50.080
It just feels very strange.

30:53.550 --> 30:55.000
Do you know what B2B is?

30:56.830 --> 30:57.790
B2B?

31:00.590 --> 31:01.920
It means

31:01.920 --> 31:03.550
box-to-box midfielder.

31:08.520 --> 31:10.980
A box-to-box midfielder is Total Football,

31:11.310 --> 31:13.310
with a huge defensive running range

31:13.750 --> 31:16.350
and being able to appear
anywhere on the field.

31:18.830 --> 31:20.530
Tactically speaking,

31:20.740 --> 31:22.910
this person has to organize
both attack and defense.

31:22.910 --> 31:23.980
He is

31:24.010 --> 31:25.670
the absolute core of the team.

31:26.680 --> 31:27.240
Me?

31:27.720 --> 31:28.440
You.

31:28.960 --> 31:31.000
You will be the brain
of Hongjing No. 8 High,

31:31.000 --> 31:33.060
thinking about the team's problems.

31:35.590 --> 31:36.310
Can I?

31:39.480 --> 31:40.440
First of all,

31:40.960 --> 31:43.020
you have to convince your teammates.

31:47.240 --> 31:48.590
My teammates?

31:54.950 --> 31:55.840
Wait,

31:55.870 --> 31:57.260
what do you mean, Wen Chengye?

31:57.260 --> 31:58.660
Which midfielder do you want to replace?

31:58.660 --> 31:59.340
Fu?

32:00.070 --> 32:01.870
What about Fu if you replace him?

32:02.510 --> 32:05.410
Controlling the midfield means
controlling the entire game.

32:05.410 --> 32:06.250
Coach,

32:07.110 --> 32:08.310
can Wen Chengye do it?

32:09.790 --> 32:10.480
Sure.

32:11.770 --> 32:12.640
Coach,

32:12.660 --> 32:15.110
do you also think Fu
should give up his position?

32:15.110 --> 32:15.880
But it's true

32:16.550 --> 32:17.930
that in our last match,

32:17.950 --> 32:19.680
Fu played as a defender, right?

32:23.310 --> 32:25.240
Fu indeed

32:25.260 --> 32:27.660
showed his strength on the defensive line.

32:31.830 --> 32:33.070
You don't agree.

32:33.600 --> 32:36.040
Is it because you are used
to the previous lineup,

32:36.040 --> 32:37.880
or because Wen Chengye
is replacing Fu Xinshu,

32:37.880 --> 32:39.410
so you feel uncomfortable?

32:45.440 --> 32:46.370
It's my problem.

32:51.570 --> 32:53.700
I'm not good at the defender position.

33:06.560 --> 33:08.690
Everyone actually knows it very well.

33:08.830 --> 33:09.920
I don't have a sense of teamwork.

33:09.920 --> 33:11.110
I prefer to play solo

33:11.140 --> 33:13.350
and only have the opponent's half
in my eyes.

33:13.350 --> 33:14.880
If you ask me to defend well,

33:15.160 --> 33:17.090
I'll feel uncomfortable all over.

33:17.200 --> 33:18.130
On the contrary,

33:19.160 --> 33:21.360
Fu Xinshu has a great sense of teamwork.

33:21.580 --> 33:22.510
He is meticulous

33:22.620 --> 33:24.150
and has a big-picture view.

33:25.120 --> 33:27.720
He can be the mainstay
of our backline defense.

33:35.720 --> 33:38.180
I believe that switching positions
with him

33:38.350 --> 33:40.550
will definitely be better for the team.

33:40.920 --> 33:41.670
Wen Chengye,

33:43.410 --> 33:44.410
after the winter break,

33:44.410 --> 33:46.210
we will be facing Shenhai Yinbo.

33:46.920 --> 33:48.710
That might be our last match.

33:48.740 --> 33:49.800
Are you confident?

33:50.370 --> 33:51.230
No.

33:51.370 --> 33:52.500
But I will work hard.

34:02.500 --> 34:03.300
I agree.

34:05.260 --> 34:06.170
I agree too.

34:06.680 --> 34:08.830
As a goalkeeper, I can see more clearly.

34:08.830 --> 34:09.800
With Fu in the back,

34:09.800 --> 34:11.440
I feel more confident.

34:29.850 --> 34:30.889
I agree too.

34:31.639 --> 34:32.540
Let's...

34:33.330 --> 34:34.560
get along well then.

34:41.449 --> 34:47.800
[Sports Equipment Room]

34:57.110 --> 34:58.030
Ms. Lin,

34:58.090 --> 35:02.130
[Football Is for Victory]

34:58.550 --> 35:00.280
I'm here to hand in my homework.

35:00.960 --> 35:02.850
We don't play football for applause,

35:02.850 --> 35:04.130
or for trophies,

35:04.780 --> 35:06.050
but to prove

35:06.080 --> 35:07.880
that we can beat our past selves.

35:10.040 --> 35:11.780
Matches are for victory.

35:11.810 --> 35:13.010
Next time,

35:12.250 --> 35:13.160
[Football is for victory,
not for applause]

35:13.180 --> 35:14.020
[or for trophies, but to prove]

35:13.510 --> 35:14.630
we will definitely win.

35:14.040 --> 35:15.260
[that we can beat our past selves.]

35:23.440 --> 35:24.190
Wen Chengye.

35:50.670 --> 35:52.470
The shoes are from a minor brand,

35:52.480 --> 35:54.320
and they're not a limited edition.

35:54.320 --> 35:55.710
I bought them with money
from my part-time job.

35:55.710 --> 35:56.910
I hope you don't mind.

36:07.230 --> 36:08.440
You gave me a gift,

36:08.440 --> 36:10.440
but I don't have money to buy you one.

36:11.000 --> 36:12.150
Then when we grow up,

36:12.150 --> 36:13.240
you can buy me one.

36:13.270 --> 36:14.020
Okay.

36:27.570 --> 36:28.250
Try them on.

37:29.600 --> 37:30.320
Boss,

37:30.440 --> 37:32.320
you went to the supermarket
just to buy boiled eggs,

37:32.320 --> 37:33.680
also for Wen Chengye?

37:33.960 --> 37:35.230
Do you feel bad for injuring him

37:35.230 --> 37:36.110
when you kicked him?

37:36.110 --> 37:37.030
Nonsense.

37:37.440 --> 37:38.670
I bought them to eat.

37:39.920 --> 37:40.760
Boss,

37:40.760 --> 37:43.690
it's not embarrassing
to care about your teammates.

37:43.960 --> 37:44.710
Eat or not?

37:46.110 --> 37:47.400
I'll eat.

37:49.630 --> 37:50.630
Let me tell you,

37:52.150 --> 37:53.070
I bought the boiled eggs,

37:53.070 --> 37:54.280
but definitely not to yield
to Wen Chengye,

37:54.280 --> 37:54.840
you know?

37:56.550 --> 37:58.360
It's because he plays well.

37:58.710 --> 38:00.570
I'm just thinking about the team.

38:00.770 --> 38:01.730
Understood,

38:01.760 --> 38:02.630
big picture.

38:04.710 --> 38:05.880
Big picture.

38:23.280 --> 38:24.140
Okay, let's go.

38:27.870 --> 38:28.920
♪ A starlit night ♪

38:29.760 --> 38:34.240
♪ Secrets falling into my palm ♪

38:34.230 --> 38:35.550
-Good, come on.
-Come on!

38:35.050 --> 38:36.290
♪ Unraveling the mystery ♪

38:35.550 --> 38:36.800
Good, let's continue.

38:36.800 --> 38:37.400
Good.

38:37.090 --> 38:41.120
♪ It was you who gave me this brilliance ♪

38:38.630 --> 38:40.430
Speed up your movement, Zhi Hui.

38:42.150 --> 38:43.330
♪ Lasting memories ♪

38:44.260 --> 38:48.580
♪ The distance
that brings our dreams closer ♪

38:49.360 --> 38:50.260
♪ To run toward you ♪

38:50.910 --> 38:55.410
♪ I keep practicing with no turning back ♪

38:58.960 --> 39:00.240
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

39:01.430 --> 39:02.760
♪ Because you're with me ♪

39:01.960 --> 39:02.920
-Come on.
-Okay.

39:04.840 --> 39:05.670
Right.

39:05.910 --> 39:07.160
♪ The light shimmers ♪

39:08.610 --> 39:09.900
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

39:11.520 --> 39:12.580
♪ Running towards you ♪

39:13.430 --> 39:14.540
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

39:18.580 --> 39:19.490
♪ Walk side by side ♪

39:20.390 --> 39:22.030
♪ Become ourselves ♪

39:24.430 --> 39:25.460
♪ Amid the storm ♪

39:26.200 --> 39:30.480
♪ As our breaths slowly intertwine ♪

39:31.190 --> 39:32.310
♪ Heartbeats alternating ♪

39:33.350 --> 39:37.590
♪ A chemistry about to emerge ♪

39:38.540 --> 39:39.470
♪ The stars are shining ♪

39:40.260 --> 39:44.780
♪ Take my hand and run forward ♪

39:43.230 --> 39:44.160
Come on, come on.

39:45.670 --> 39:46.520
♪ For you ♪

39:47.410 --> 39:52.020
♪ I'm willing to
keep practicing and practicing ♪

39:55.430 --> 39:56.990
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

39:57.520 --> 39:58.670
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

39:58.360 --> 40:00.230
Welcome to the Youth Super League.

39:58.700 --> 39:59.890
[Hongjing No. 8 High vs Shenhai Yinbo]

40:00.230 --> 40:02.400
A crucial match of the league
is about to begin.

40:02.400 --> 40:03.800
The dark horse, Hongjing No. 8 High,

40:03.800 --> 40:05.400
will face the traditionally strong team
Shenhai Yinbo

40:05.400 --> 40:08.320
with a neat lineup.

40:08.320 --> 40:10.400
If Hongjing No. 8 High
wants to enter the finals,

40:10.400 --> 40:11.550
they can't afford to lose this match.

40:11.550 --> 40:13.010
Take it easy. Take it easy.

40:14.280 --> 40:15.740
Keep your eyes on the ball!

40:16.630 --> 40:18.110
Just 3 minutes into the game,

40:18.110 --> 40:21.550
and Shenhai Yinbo has created
a threat with their speed!

40:23.320 --> 40:25.920
Why did Yinbo
get a corner kick right away?

40:26.800 --> 40:28.320
Their corner kick tactics

40:28.880 --> 40:30.140
are very distinctive.

40:30.360 --> 40:32.120
This is our last chance to qualify.

40:32.120 --> 40:33.580
We absolutely can't lose.

40:37.170 --> 40:39.170
You've been wearing red for so long.

40:39.600 --> 40:41.460
You even resorted to this method.

40:41.760 --> 40:42.760
Do you have so little confidence

40:42.760 --> 40:44.120
in us?

40:45.360 --> 40:46.420
It's not like that.

40:49.960 --> 40:51.820
Although the opponent is strong,

40:52.360 --> 40:53.400
we have

40:53.400 --> 40:54.230
flow.

41:09.480 --> 41:10.230
Yeah.

41:10.840 --> 41:13.170
There is a word in psychology called flow.

41:13.960 --> 41:17.200
It refers to the high level
of excitement and satisfaction

41:17.200 --> 41:20.110
brought about
by being fully engaged in a task.

41:20.140 --> 41:22.290
Both their displayed professionalism

41:22.290 --> 41:23.810
and achieved results

41:23.840 --> 41:26.140
will surpass their usual baseline.

41:26.160 --> 41:29.090
Many athletes have experienced
the feeling of flow.

41:29.800 --> 41:31.000
It's probably

41:31.000 --> 41:33.030
like having a hot hand
on the basketball court,

41:33.030 --> 41:34.230
making every shot.

41:35.370 --> 41:37.600
Would it work

41:37.630 --> 41:39.090
on the football field too?

41:39.880 --> 41:41.170
On the football field,

41:41.550 --> 41:43.250
they are fully focused,

41:43.590 --> 41:45.360
as if entering their own world.

41:45.880 --> 41:47.240
Every touch of the ball

41:47.260 --> 41:48.860
is accurate.

41:48.890 --> 41:50.290
Every pass

41:50.320 --> 41:52.250
anticipates his teammate's runs.

41:52.550 --> 41:54.060
On the field today,

41:54.520 --> 41:56.280
I saw their flow.

41:56.340 --> 41:59.020
♪ Who hasn't known
the dark of night and uncertainty? ♪

42:00.020 --> 42:03.380
♪ Stumbling, covered in wounds,
losing direction ♪

42:03.710 --> 42:05.800
From these defenses, we can see that,

42:04.190 --> 42:09.870
♪ Wandering alone,
gaining strength through pain ♪

42:05.800 --> 42:08.440
in order for Hongjing No. 8 High
to win today's match,

42:08.440 --> 42:10.390
the players have raised their focus

42:10.390 --> 42:11.750
to the extreme.

42:12.480 --> 42:15.510
♪ Riding the wind,
chasing an unknown horizon ♪

42:13.550 --> 42:15.550
Hongjing No. 8 High launches
a quick counterattack.

42:15.550 --> 42:17.480
Their teamwork is surprisingly good today.

42:16.550 --> 42:19.910
♪ Looking up,
dreaming side by side of great ideals ♪

42:17.480 --> 42:18.800
A beautiful through ball!

42:18.800 --> 42:20.000
No. 7 gets the ball.

42:20.000 --> 42:21.230
Chen Jianghe holds off his opponent

42:20.630 --> 42:26.460
♪ The vast world
awaits youth to arrive ♪

42:21.230 --> 42:22.600
and passes the ball out.

42:23.400 --> 42:24.190
Wang Fa,

42:24.760 --> 42:26.030
do we have a chance?

42:27.210 --> 42:30.000
♪ If braving the wind
and waves ♪

42:28.480 --> 42:29.510
Wen Chengye!

42:29.510 --> 42:30.550
Wen Chengye takes the ball

42:30.550 --> 42:31.550
and relies on his personal ability

42:30.960 --> 42:33.490
♪ What it takes to grow ♪

42:31.550 --> 42:33.070
to tear apart Yinbo's defense.

42:33.070 --> 42:34.280
He passes it to Lin Lu.

42:34.280 --> 42:35.840
He shoots from a distance!

42:35.050 --> 42:37.530
♪ I will stubbornly
go against the current ♪

42:38.590 --> 42:40.940
♪ And let myself go wild ♪

42:41.800 --> 42:43.070
It's in!

42:42.300 --> 42:45.150
♪ No matter how long the road ahead ♪

42:43.070 --> 42:44.110
One to zero!

42:44.480 --> 42:47.030
A perfect team play
by Hongjing No. 8 High!

42:46.520 --> 42:48.870
♪ Nothing can stop me ♪

42:47.030 --> 42:49.710
In the 87th minute of the match,

42:49.710 --> 42:51.110
they changed the score.

42:50.550 --> 42:51.510
♪ Break through every haze of doubt ♪

42:51.110 --> 42:53.760
One to zero basically seals the victory!

42:52.540 --> 42:53.760
♪ Chase the light within me ♪

42:53.760 --> 42:55.750
-Great!
-Good!

42:55.040 --> 42:57.080
♪ Strong wings grow through the storm ♪

42:55.770 --> 42:56.790
Nice shot!

42:58.240 --> 43:01.050
♪ Even if no one cheers ♪

43:02.200 --> 43:04.340
♪ I'll keep fighting my way through ♪

43:06.120 --> 43:07.680
♪ On a deserted battlefield ♪

43:08.640 --> 43:09.780
♪ Thrive and bloom ♪

43:10.650 --> 43:13.590
♪ I'll take every scar ♪

43:11.590 --> 43:14.840
We won! We won!

43:14.510 --> 43:17.410
♪ As my badge of honor ♪

43:15.320 --> 43:18.550
-Nice!
-Goal!

43:31.080 --> 43:33.840
♪ If braving the wind
and waves ♪

43:34.750 --> 43:38.060
♪ What it takes to grow ♪

43:38.840 --> 43:41.470
♪ I will stubbornly
go against the current ♪

43:42.380 --> 43:45.300
♪ And let myself go wild ♪
